main event: A witness in Washington, D.C. observed a single bright, illuminated saucer-shaped object moving silently and maneuvering in an impossible way for any known aircraft in 1966.
interesting points: The object appeared to be under intelligent control and maneuvered in a way impossible for any known aircraft.
The object was a solid saucer shape and illuminated from within.
The witness observed the object for about 11 minutes.
The object moved behind and in front of a hazy cloud during the sighting.
The witness estimated the object's angular size to be about 1/6 of a match stick held at arm's length.
sighted object: a single bright, illuminated saucer-shaped object
